description:
"Difficult Climbing Game offers a more streamlined and easier climbing experience compared to other climbing games, yet it remains captivating. Use "shifts" to grab and the "up" to lift yourself to the top. Reach the summit in record time and see your name rise on the leaderboard. Let's see who's the fastest climber in the world. This game is the easiest and fastest about climbing.

-Various beautiful settings
-No distractions, pure gameplay
-A non-violent, relaxing atmosphere
-Climb to the top, fall into the water, and try again
